2026-05-15T07:07:35.4079599Z 254            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-15T07:07:35.4079957Z 255            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-15T07:07:35.4080305Z 256            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
